      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *
      ** +--- Start of Main processing -------------------------------+
      ** �                                                            �
      ** � *INZSR is executed at program activation.                  �
      ** �                                                            �
      ** +------------------------------------------------------------+
      *
      ** Initialise work variable.
      *
     C                   EVAL      IDx = 0
      *
      ** Validate nature of account
      *
     C                   EXSR      SRValNatAc
      *
      ** If an error has been found, set return code appropriately.
      ** Otherwise, update valid file fields.
      *
     C                   IF        OKNATU = 'N'
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = 'ERROR'
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   IF        OKNATU <> 'N'
     C                   MOVEL     DDNATU        S1NATU
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   RETURN
      *
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRValNatAc - Validation for Nature of Account                *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     SRValNatAc    BEGSR
      *
      ** Nature of account is mandatory.
      *
     C                   IF        DDNATU = *BLANKS
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKNATU
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDNATU'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0243'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   GOTO      EValNatAc
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Question mark is valid only on repair and i/c screens input.
      *

     C     '?'           SCAN      DDNATU                                 01

     C                   IF        *IN01 = *ON

     C                   IF        PMode = '*FRONT'
     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKNATU
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDNATU'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0244'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   GOTO      EValNatAc
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   EVAL      PReDsp = 'Y'
     C                   ENDIF
      *
      ** Nature of account must be a valid customer.
      *
     C                   CALL      'AONATUR0'
     C                   PARM      *BLANKS       PRtCd
     C                   PARM      '*KEY   '     POptn
     C                   PARM      DDNATU        PNtAc
     C     SDNATU        PARM      SDNATU        DSFDY

     C                   IF        PRtCd <> *BLANKS
     C                   IF        PRtCd = '*NOSEL '
     C                   EVAL      DDNATU = *BLANKS
     C                   ENDIF

     C                   MOVE      'N'           OKNATU
     C                   ADD       1             IDx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDNATU'      FldNamXAr(IDx)
     C                   MOVEL     'SEA0244'     MsgIdXAr(IDx)
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVEL     TNNATU        DDNATU
     C                   ENDIF

     C     EValNatAc     ENDSR

      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Program Initialisation                              *
      *         - This subroutine runs automatically for program      *
      *           initialisation.                                     *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************

     C     *INZSR        BEGSR

     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      *
      ** INPUT
      ** =====
      *
      ** Return code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
      *
      ** Securities screen 3 details from incoming transaction
      ** - screen format
     C                   PARM                    NwSE3ScnFmt
      *
      ** Mode = '*FRONT' (Front Office Transaction Interface)
      ** Mode = '      ' (Not Front Office Transaction Interface)
      ** Mode = '*SIN  ' (Screen input function)
      ** Mode = '*RPR  ' (Repair function)
     C                   PARM                    PMode
      *
      ** Redisplay screen
     C                   PARM                    PReDsp
      *
      ** OUTPUT
      ** ======
      *
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      *
      ** Securities Screen 3 error indicators
     C                   PARM                    SEESEC3
      *
      ** Securities for file update - file format
     C                   PARM                    NwSEFilFmt
      *
      ** Program, module and procedure names for dbase error processing
      ** ==============================================================
      ** The following /COPY sets these values.
      *
      /COPY ZACPYSRC,DBFIELDS

     C                   ENDSR

